    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly, and all major mechanical systems are in solid working order. While the exterior retains a nice finish, you will find some minor stone chips on the hood and a few light scratches consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, though there is some light wear on the driver's seat bolster. It\u2019s a reliable, attractive car that is ready for its next owner to drive away with confidence.",
